'''谢伊文特·艾希安·吉爾傑斯-亞歷山大'''（{{lang-en|Shaivonte Aician Gilgeous-Alexander}}，{{bd|1998年|7月12日}}）是加拿大职业[[篮球运动员|篮球运动员]]，现效力于[[NBA|NBA]][[俄克拉荷马城雷霆|俄克拉荷马城雷霆]]。

吉尔杰斯-亚历山大在[[2018年NBA选秀|2018年NBA选秀]]中被[[夏洛特黄蜂|夏洛特黄蜂]]选中，并旋即交易至[[洛杉矶快船|洛杉矶快船]]。在快船度过新秀赛季后，吉尔杰斯-亚历山大入选了当年的[[NBA最佳新秀阵容|NBA最佳新秀阵容第二阵容]]。但在之后他和队友[[达尼罗·加里纳利|达尼罗·加里纳利]]被交易至俄克拉荷马城雷霆以换取前锋[[保罗·乔治|保罗·乔治]]。

== 早年生活 ==
谢伊·吉尔杰斯-亚历山大于1998年7月12日出生在加拿大[[安大略省|安大略省]]的[[多伦多|多伦多]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.fiba.com/pages/eng/fa/player/p/pid/128563/sid/8094/tid/257/tid2//_/2016_FIBA_Americas_U18_Championship_for_Men/index.html|title=Shai Gilgeous-Alexander profile, FIBA Americas U18 Championship for Men 2016 {{!}} FIBA.COM|work=FIBA.COM|access-date=2021-03-29}}</ref>。他的母亲，{{link-en|查曼因·吉尔杰斯|Charmaine Gilgeous}}曾是一位[[短跑|短跑]]运动员，曾代表[[安提瓜和巴布达|安提瓜和巴布达]]参加过[[1992年夏季奥运会|1992年夏季奥运会]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/hamilton/hamilton-shai-gilgeous-alexander-1.4714498|title=Hamilton point guard Shai Gilgeous-Alexander a top prospect in NBA draft {{!}} CBC News|work=CBC|access-date=2021-03-29|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190409071152/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/hamilton/hamilton-shai-gilgeous-alexander-1.4714498|dead-url=no}}</ref>。谢伊的父亲沃恩·亚历山大则是他少年时期的教练<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.kentucky.com/sports/college/kentucky-sports/uk-basketball-men/article189644684.html|title=Competitive cousins shared a room in high school. UK-Virginia Tech game pits them against each other.|work=kentucky|access-date=2021-03-29|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130142730/https://www.kentucky.com/sports/college/kentucky-sports/uk-basketball-men/article189644684.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在安大略省[[汉密尔顿_(加拿大)|汉密尔顿]]的圣托马斯·莫尔天主教中学开始了高中生活，之后转到阿兰·麦克纳布爵士中学继续学习。谢伊之后又再次转学至[[美国|美国]][[田纳西州|田纳西州]][[查塔努加|查塔努加]]的汉密尔顿高地基督学院以精进自己的篮球技术。在那里，吉尔杰斯-亚历山大度过了高三和高四的两年，并于2017年毕业<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.timesfreepress.com/news/sports/columns/story/2018/jun/21/wiedmer-hamiltheights-coach-hopes-see-former/473528/|title=Wiedmer: Hamilton Heights coach hopes to see former player Shai Gilgeous-Alexander become NBA lottery pick|work=Chattanooga Times Free Press|access-date=2018-06-21|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190712095439/https://www.timesfreepress.com/news/sports/columns/story/2018/jun/21/wiedmer-hamiltheights-coach-hopes-see-former/473528/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://amp.timesfreepress.com/news/sports/college/story/2018/mar/11/former-hamiltheights-player-now-star-kentucky/465643/|title=Former Hamilton Heights player now a star at Kentucky|work=Chattanooga Times Free Press|access-date=2018-06-21|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180621194307/http://amp.timesfreepress.com/news/sports/college/story/2018/mar/11/former-hamiltheights-player-now-star-kentucky/465643/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 高中生涯 ==
吉尔杰斯-亚历山大在九年级时并没能进入圣托马斯·莫尔天主教中学的主力阵容，所以只能从它的下级队打起，但他最终为球队赢得了当年市的下级队冠军，个人则当选MVP<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.toronto.com/sports-story/8684906-hamilton-s-shai-gilgeous-alexander-about-to-star-on-nba-stage/|title=Hamilton's Shai Gilgeous-Alexander about to star on NBA stage|last=Radley|first=Scott|date=2018-06-20|work=Toronto.com|access-date=2018-06-21|language=en-CA}}</ref>。之后谢伊转学到阿兰·麦克纳布爵士中学，又在2015年来到[[美国|美国]][[田纳西州|田纳西州]][[查塔努加|查塔努加]]的汉密尔顿高地基督学院<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://basketballrecruiting.rivals.com/news/alexander-to-florida|title=BasketballRecruiting.Rivals.com - Alexander to Florida|date=2015-11-27|access-date=2021-03-31|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024145047/https://basketballrecruiting.rivals.com/news/alexander-to-florida|dead-url=no}}</ref>。谢伊说，他来到查塔努加是为了打上更高级别的比赛。在他最后一个高中赛季，吉尔杰斯-亚历山大场均能贡献18.8分、4.4个篮板球并送出4次助攻<ref name="Kentucky">{{Cite news|url=https://www.kentucky.com/sports/college/kentucky-sports/uk-basketball-men/article177166321.html|title=After many forks in the road, Shai Gilgeous-Alexander found a basketball home at UK|last=Tipton|first=Jerry|date=2017-10-05|work=Kentucky.com|access-date=2018-06-21|language=en-CA|archive-date=2019-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190920195008/https://www.kentucky.com/sports/college/kentucky-sports/uk-basketball-men/article177166321.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 在2016年年初，吉尔杰斯-亚历山大参加了当年的{{link-en|篮球无疆界|Basketball Without Borders}}训练营<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://northpolehoops.com/2016/11/01/kentucky-offers-shai-alexander-after-reopening-recruitment/|title=Kentucky Offers Shai Alexander After Reopening Recruitment|date=2016-11-01|website=Northpolehoops.com|access-date=2021-03-31|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926220603/http://northpolehoops.com/2016/11/01/kentucky-offers-shai-alexander-after-reopening-recruitment/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

作为[[ESPN|ESPN]]评定的四星高中生，谢伊一开始承诺加入[[佛罗里达大学|佛罗里达大学]]，但他在2016年10月反悔了这一决定<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.espn.com/college-sports/recruiting/basketball/mens/story/_/id/18045597/former-florida-gators-commit-shai-alexander-chooses-kentucky-wildcats|title=Ex-Florida commit Alexander picks Kentucky|work=ESPN.com|access-date=2021-03-31|archive-date=2019-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190712095443/https://www.espn.com/college-sports/recruiting/basketball/mens/story/_/id/18045597/former-florida-gators-commit-shai-alexander-chooses-kentucky-wildcats|dead-url=no}}</ref>。谢伊之后又将他的择校目标锁定在了[[肯塔基大学|肯塔基大学]]、[[堪萨斯大学|堪萨斯大学]]、[[雪城大学|雪城大学]]、[[德克萨斯大学奥斯汀分校|德克萨斯大学奥斯汀分校]]和[[内华达大学拉斯维加斯分校|内华达大学拉斯维加斯分校]]之间<ref name="Kentucky"/>。11月，谢伊决定加入肯塔基大学征战[[NCAA|NCAA]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.espn.com/college-sports/recruiting/basketball/mens/story/_/id/18045597/former-florida-gators-commit-shai-alexander-chooses-kentucky-wildcats|title=Ex-Florida commit Alexander picks Kentucky|work=ESPN.com|access-date=2021-03-11|archive-date=2019-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190712095443/https://www.espn.com/college-sports/recruiting/basketball/mens/story/_/id/18045597/former-florida-gators-commit-shai-alexander-chooses-kentucky-wildcats|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2017年{{link-en|耐克篮球峰会|Nike Hoop Summit}}上，谢伊代表世界队出场21分24秒，得到11分<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.usab.com/mens/nike-hoop-summit/stats.aspx|title=Nike Hoop Summit|access-date=2021-03-31|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205150254/https://www.usab.com/mens/nike-hoop-summit/stats.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 大学生涯 ==
吉尔杰斯-亚历山大以替补的身份开始了他的[[NCAA|大学篮球]]生涯，他先是作为一年级后卫{{link-en|奎德·格林|Quade Green}}的后备出战。在一场对阵[[UCLA|UCLA]]的惨败之后，谢伊在面对[[路易斯维尔大学|路易斯维尔大学]]的比赛中得到了24分和5个篮板球，并送出4次助攻和3次抢断<ref name="ESPN">{{cite web|title=Shai Gilgeous-Alexander|url=http://www.espn.com/mens-college-basketball/player/_/id/4278073/shai-gilgeous-alexander|website=ESPN.com|access-date=2021-04-02|archive-date=2018-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180621062714/http://www.espn.com/mens-college-basketball/player/_/id/4278073/shai-gilgeous-alexander|dead-url=no}}</ref>。谢伊之后被从板凳席提上首发阵容，与未来在NBA的队友{{link-en|哈米杜·迪亚洛|Hamidou Diallo}}搭档后场。谢伊为此剪掉了来到肯塔基大学以后一直留的长发<ref>{{cite web|last1=Tucker|first1=Kyle|title=Kentucky basketball: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander cuts his hair, then carves up Louisville|url=https://www.seccountry.com/kentucky/kentucky-basketball-shai-gilgeous-alexander-burns-louisville|website=SEC Country|access-date=2021-04-02|archive-date=2018-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180616212729/https://www.seccountry.com/kentucky/kentucky-basketball-shai-gilgeous-alexander-burns-louisville|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在得到先发位置后，谢伊继续出色发挥，他在之后面对[[喬治亞大學|乔治亚]]和[[路易斯安那州立大學|路易斯安那州立大學]]时分别得到了21分和18分。之后肯塔基大学的状态低迷，一路遭遇四连败，但吉尔杰斯-亚历山大在与另外四名新人搭档的首发阵容表现出色。他在常规赛季能场均贡献12.9分、3.8个篮板球和4.6次助攻<ref name="ESPN"/>。

之后肯塔基大学在[[东南联盟|东南联盟]]锦标赛中夺得了赛区冠军，吉尔杰斯-亚历山大荣膺MVP奖项。在NCAA锦标赛中，肯塔基大学在64和32强中淘汰了{{link-en|戴维森学院|Davidson College}}和[[布法罗大学|布法罗大学]]，但在“甜蜜16强”的比赛中输给了[[堪薩斯州立大學|堪薩斯州立大學]]，吉尔杰斯-亚历山大在最后时刻错失了扳平比分的压哨三分球。这成为了他大学篮球生涯的最后一幕，因为他在2018年4月9日宣布离开学校，参加[[2018年NBA选秀|2018年NBA选秀]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Givony|first1=Jonathan|title=Kentucky freshman guard Shai Gilgeous-Alexander to enter draft|url=http://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/23094736/shai-gilgeous-alexander-kentucky-wildcats-entering-nba-draft|access-date=2021-04-02|work=ESPN|date=2018-04-09|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109035650/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/23094736/shai-gilgeous-alexander-kentucky-wildcats-entering-nba-draft|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 职业生涯 ==
=== 洛杉矶快船时期 ===
2018年NBA选秀上，谢伊·吉尔杰斯-亚历山大在第11顺位被[[夏洛特黄蜂|夏洛特黄蜂]]选中。他的签约权旋即被交易至[[洛杉矶快船|洛杉矶快船]]，以换取第12号选秀权（被用于选中{{link-en|迈尔斯·布里奇斯|Miles Bridges}}）和两个未来的二轮选秀权<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cbc.ca/sports/basketball/nba/canadian-gilgeous-alexander-nba-draft-1.4717462|title=19-year-old Canadian goes 11th in NBA draft|work=CBC|access-date=2021-04-02|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190409071155/https://www.cbc.ca/sports/basketball/nba/canadian-gilgeous-alexander-nba-draft-1.4717462|dead-url=no}}</ref>。谢伊为快船出战了当年的夏季联赛，场均得到19分、4.8个篮板球、4次助攻和2.3次抢断<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nba.com/clippers/news/2018-summer-league-recap|title=Rookies Gilgeous-Alexander & Robinson Shine at NBA Summer League|work=NBA.com|access-date=2021-04-02|language=en-US|date=2018-07-16|archive-date=2018-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180913182948/https://www.nba.com/clippers/news/2018-summer-league-recap|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年10月17日，吉尔杰斯-亚历山大完成了他在[[NBA|NBA]]的处子秀。在面对[[丹佛掘金|丹佛掘金]]的赛季揭幕战中，谢伊出战28分钟，6投5中得到11分并送出4次助攻。在12月17日和2019年1月18日面对[[波特兰开拓者|波特兰开拓者]]和[[金州勇士|金州勇士]]的比赛中，谢伊两次得到个人常规赛最高的24分<ref name="2019shai">{{cite web|url=https://www.basketball-reference.com/players/g/gilgesh01/gamelog/2019|title=Shai Gilgeous-Alexander 2018-19 Game Log|work=basketballreference.com|access-date=2021-04-02|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117001817/https://www.basketball-reference.com/players/g/gilgesh01/gamelog/2019/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月29日，谢伊以国际队球员身份入选了当年的[[NBA全明星新秀赛|NBA全明星新秀赛]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nba.com/article/2019/01/29/2019-mtn-dew-ice-rising-stars-roster-official-release|title=Doncic, Simmons headline Mtn Dew Ice Rising Stars rosters|website=NBA.com|date=2019-01-30|language=en-US|accessdate=2021-04-02|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929231758/https://www.nba.com/article/2019/01/29/2019-mtn-dew-ice-rising-stars-roster-official-release|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他在赛中得到了15分、5个篮板球和6次助攻<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.basketball-reference.com/players/g/gilgesh01/gamelog/2019|title=2019 NBA Rising Stars Team USA 161, Team World 144|work=basketballreference.com|access-date=2021-04-02|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117001817/https://www.basketball-reference.com/players/g/gilgesh01/gamelog/2019/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月21日，在面对金州勇士的[[2019年NBA季後賽|2019年季后赛]]首轮比赛中，吉尔杰斯-亚历山大得到了生涯最高的25分<ref name="2019shai"/>。

=== 俄克拉荷马城雷霆时期 ===
2019年7月10日，快船宣布将谢伊·吉尔杰斯-亚历山大、[[达尼罗·加里纳利|达尼罗·加里纳利]]、5个未来的首轮选秀权和2个首轮选秀权的互换权交易至雷霆以换取全明星球员[[保罗·乔治|保罗·乔治]]<ref>{{cite press release|title=L.A. Clippers Acquire Six-Time NBA All-Star Paul George|date=2019-07-10|publisher=Los Angeles Clippers|url=https://www.nba.com/clippers/clippers-acquire-six-time-nba-all-star-paul-george|access-date=2021-04-02|archive-date=2021-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130045004/https://www.nba.com/clippers/clippers-acquire-six-time-nba-all-star-paul-george|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

10月23日，吉尔杰斯-亚历山大完成了代表雷霆的常规赛首秀，他在对阵[[犹他爵士|犹他爵士]]的比赛中得到生涯新高的26分和2个篮板球<ref name="2020shai">{{cite web|url=https://www.basketball-reference.com/players/g/gilgesh01/gamelog/2020|title=Shai Gilgeous-Alexander 2019-20 Game Log|work=basketballreference.com|access-date=2021-04-02|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126130005/https://www.basketball-reference.com/players/g/gilgesh01/gamelog/2020|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12月22日，他在击败老东家洛杉矶快船的比赛中贡献生涯新高的32分<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=401161084|title=Gilgeous-Alexander helps Thunder beat Clippers 118-112|date=219-12-22|website=ESPN.com|access-date=2021-04-02|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027192552/https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=401161084|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年1月14日，谢伊在击败[[明尼苏达森林狼|明尼苏达森林狼]]的比赛中得到了生涯首个[[三双|三双]]数据，他全场攻下20分、20个篮板球并送出10次助攻，这是NBA近三十年来除了前雷霆球星[[拉塞尔·威斯布鲁克|拉塞尔·威斯布鲁克]]以外第一位拿下20+20+10数据的球员<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/28479763/shai-gilgeous-alexander-youngest-ever-20-rebound-triple-double|title=SGA youngest ever with 20-rebound triple-double|date=2020-01-14|website=ESPN.com|language=en|access-date=2020-01-14|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803210752/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/28479763/shai-gilgeous-alexander-youngest-ever-20-rebound-triple-double|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cbssports.com/nba/news/thunders-shai-gilgeous-alexander-records-historic-first-career-triple-double-in-win-over-timberwolves/amp/|title=Thunder's Shai Gilgeous-Alexander records historic first career triple-double in win over Timberwolves|website=www.cbssports.com|language=en|access-date=2020-01-14|archive-date=2020-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116025707/https://www.cbssports.com/nba/news/thunders-shai-gilgeous-alexander-records-historic-first-career-triple-double-in-win-over-timberwolves/amp/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年7月，他与[[匡威|匡威]]签下了一份球鞋代言合同<ref>{{cite news|first=Nick|last=De Paula|url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/29425631/shai-gilgeous-alexander-signs-converse-joining-draymond-green-kelly-oubre-jr|work=ESPN.com|date=2020-07-08|accessdate=2021-04-02|title=Shai Gilgeous-Alexander signs with Converse, joining Draymond Green and Kelly Oubre Jr.|archive-date=2021-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210419225810/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/29425631/shai-gilgeous-alexander-signs-converse-joining-draymond-green-kelly-oubre-jr|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

12月26日，谢伊在面对夏洛特黄蜂的[[2020-21_NBA赛季|赛季]]揭幕战中得到24分、7个篮板球和9次助攻，并投进了生涯首个制胜进球<ref>{{cite web|url=https://clutchpoints.com/thunder-video-shai-gilgeous-alexander-hits-game-winner-with-1-4-seconds-left-on-the-clock/|title=VIDEO: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander Hits Game-Winner To End Hornets Comeback Bid|website=ClutchPoints|last=Salao|first=Renzo|access-date=2021-04-02|date=2020-12-26|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227024943/https://clutchpoints.com/thunder-video-shai-gilgeous-alexander-hits-game-winner-with-1-4-seconds-left-on-the-clock/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年2月24日，吉尔杰斯-亚历山大在面对[[圣安东尼奥马刺|圣安东尼奥马刺]]中得到了生涯新高的42分，并带领球队获胜<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.sportsnet.ca/nba/article/canadas-shai-gilgeous-alexander-career-high-42-thunder-win-spurs/| title=Canada's Shai Gilgeous-Alexander has career-high 42 in Thunder win over Spurs| website=Sportsnet| access-date=2021-04-02| date=2021-02-24| archive-date=2021-03-13| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313011820/https://www.sportsnet.ca/nba/article/canadas-shai-gilgeous-alexander-career-high-42-thunder-win-spurs/| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年8月3日，多份报道称吉尔杰斯-亚历山大已经与雷霆队达成一份价值1.72亿美元的五年续约合同<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/31945995/shai-gilgeous-alexander-agrees-5-year-172-million-maximum-rookie-contract-extension-oklahoma-city-thunder|title=Shai Gilgeous-Alexander agrees to 5-year, $172 million maximum rookie contract extension with Oklahoma City Thunder|website=ESPN|last=Young|first=Royce|access-date=2022-02-23|date=2021-08-03}}</ref>。8月6日，雷霆队官方宣布已经与吉尔杰斯-亚历山大达成多年续约<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nba.com/thunder/release/sga-contract-extension-210806|title=Thunder Signs Shai Gilgeous-Alexander to Multi-Year Contract Extension|website=NBA.com|access-date=2022-02-23|date=2021-08-06}}</ref>。

==国家队生涯==
